<section id="news">
  <title>Release 0.22 of &app;</title>

  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
	The library gets updated to the C++20 language version, and
	requires gcc 10.
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
	Redesigned
	<link linkend="serialization">Serialization API</link>
	to be const-correct.
	Cleaned up <acronym>HTTP</acronym>
	<link linkend="httpuseragent">client</link>
	and
	<link linkend="httpserver">server</link> API, replacing camel-case
	methods with standardized names.
      </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>
	Added support for the TLS ALPN extension.
      </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
      <para>
	New templates: <link linkend="rangevector"><classname>&ns;::sorted_range</classname></link>,
	and <link linkend="explicitrefptr"><classname>&ns;::explicit_arg</classname></link>.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>

